name: leeds-housing-options-monthly-enquiries
notes:
Leeds Housing Options is the council's advice service for those who are homeless, at risk of homelessness, or simply wanting advice about the available housing options.  The council will do everything it can if you are homeless or at risk of becoming homeless, to help you stay where you are or find alternative accommodation.

This dataset shows the number of presentations to the Leeds Housing Options service and the reasons why they presented.

ADDITIONAL INFORMATION

  • Further information about the service can be found at the following website:
  • http://www.leeds.gov.uk/residents/pages/leeds-housing-options.aspx
title: Leeds Housing Options monthly enquiries
